  Solistus Da`Krun <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=waldenawildfyre>Waldena Wildfyre</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master Summoner</span><br>  Posts: 282<br> <font color=#333333>(5/16/01 12:24:15 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm27.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=35.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Mage VS Necro duel</span><hr size=1> Get good MR so he cant fear or darkness you.  Fighting in an arena is also makes it alot easier;  No room to be kited.  Basicly ya gotta kill the necro before the dots kill you, not too hard with good MR.  Or stay alive long enough for your pet to tear through the necro pet and go beat the necro (assuming ya pet isnt feared).  Also good to leave first few buff slots open so ya can dispell any effects ya get.  Also if ya can get good DR or PR resistance to go along with good MR, that should help. <p><table border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1">
